{"tid":1018243,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"KPOP大勢女團於三月回歸","createTime":"2019-02-12T06:08:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T17:17:47.000Z","uid":74065,"like":7,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"cb04d5d5283d6dc2bd9b4246816dd1ca279f5591","tid":1018243,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T06:08:41.000Z","msg":"MOMOLAND將於3月回歸,繼續大勢步伐<br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/f48d11ca43d3ee132461b19917a22620/tumblr_ovmtoudaQH1ueg2m0o2_500.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Ff48d11ca43d3ee132461b19917a22620%2Ftumblr_ovmtoudaQH1ueg2m0o2_500.gif&h=4f5345b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女子團體MOMOLAND將於3月回歸。<br />\n<br />\n12日,據starnews的採訪結果,MOMOLAND 確定將於3月發行新專輯,目前正在為回歸做準備。在往返於韓國和日本的繁忙行程中,也爲回歸而忙碌著。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.allkpop.com/upload/2018/01/af_org/03110110/momoland.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.allkpop.com%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2Faf_org%2F03110110%2Fmomoland.jpg&h=2ed5a567&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMOMOLAND在韓國發表的最後一張專輯是去年6月26日發表的迷你專輯《Fun to The World》<br />\n。這是此前一直專注於日本活動的MOMOLAND時隔9個月發行的新專輯,預計會有很多粉絲期待<br />\n。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/images/28fcf736be7ec150b0729dbb43c273ab/tenor.gif?itemid=10102643\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.tenor.com%2Fimages%2F28fcf736be7ec150b0729dbb43c273ab%2Ftenor.gif%3Fitemid%3D10102643&h=87e088e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1972a013a67056d0d973953d9640686275a989ed","tid":1018243,"uid":223790,"like":43,"dislike":7,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T06:09:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c050c5fa716b47aa539f3517efb3351cab32b50c","tid":1018243,"uid":213300,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T06:09:16.000Z","msg":"召喚mml粉皮"},{"pid":"e5401f7f9e3c04695b43a25dec7401e75b0df16d","tid":1018243,"uid":223790,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T06:09:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}